    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  We estimated the reproduction number of 2020 Iranian COVID-19 epidemic using two different methods: R\n                  <jats:sub>0</jats:sub>\n                  was estimated at 4.4 (95% CI, 3.9, 4.9) (generalized growth model) and 3.50 (1.28, 8.14) (epidemic doubling time) (February 19 - March 1) while the effective R was estimated at 1.55 (1.06, 2.57) (March 6-19).\n                </jats:p>",
